description:
Minor amendment of planning application ref: P080525 dated 17/06/2008.  The amendments are:
A]	removal of lower and upper ground floor arrangement to provide for a ground floor level addressing the street including omission of lightwells; alteration to ground floor elevations; and creation of basement level.
B]	omission of hotel rooms at ground floor level and provision of ancillary restaurant/bar together with back of house functions at new ground floor level;
C]	lowering of floor to ceiling heights and inclusion of an additional storey within the envelope of approved building;
D]	reduction of hotel room numbers from 105 to 95;
E]	relocation of escape stair to southern boundary with N1 Centre;
F]	alteration to window/cedar panel arrangement
